    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>网易云音乐<br><a href="https://api.suiyil.cn/163-api/">https://api.suiyil.cn/163-api/</a></p><a id="more"></a><hr><p>代码源自 <a href="https://github.com/injahow/meting-api">https://github.com/injahow/meting-api</a></p><h1 id="参数"><a href="#参数" class="headerlink" title="参数"></a>参数</h1><h3 id="type-类型"><a href="#type-类型" class="headerlink" title="type: 类型"></a>type: 类型</h3><p>name 歌曲名<br>artist 歌手<br>url 链接<br>cover 封面<br>lrc 歌词<br>single 获取以上所有信息(单曲)<br>playlist 获取以上所有信息(歌单)</p><h3 id="id-网易云单曲ID或网易云歌单ID"><a href="#id-网易云单曲ID或网易云歌单ID" class="headerlink" title="id: 网易云单曲ID或网易云歌单ID"></a>id: 网易云单曲ID或网易云歌单ID</h3><h1 id="使用参考"><a href="#使用参考" class="headerlink" title="使用参考"></a>使用参考</h1><h2 id="链接使用"><a href="#链接使用" class="headerlink" title="链接使用"></a>链接使用</h2><p>歌曲url：<a href="https://api.suiyil.cn/163-api/?type=url&id=551339134">https://api.suiyil.cn/163-api/?type=url&amp;id=551339134</a><br>封面cover：<a href="https://api.suiyil.cn/163-api/?type=cover&id=551339134">https://api.suiyil.cn/163-api/?type=cover&amp;id=551339134</a><br>歌词lrc：<a href="https://api.suiyil.cn/163-api/?type=lrc&id=551339134">https://api.suiyil.cn/163-api/?type=lrc&amp;id=551339134</a><br>歌词lrc（含翻译）：<a href="https://api.suiyil.cn/163-api/index_cn.php?type=lrc&id=551339134">https://api.suiyil.cn/163-api/index_cn.php?type=lrc&amp;id=551339134</a><br>歌曲信息single：<a href="https://api.suiyil.cn/163-api/?type=single&id=551339134">https://api.suiyil.cn/163-api/?type=single&amp;id=551339134</a><br>歌单信息playlist：<a href="https://api.suiyil.cn/163-api/?type=playlist&id=5225821464">https://api.suiyil.cn/163-api/?type=playlist&amp;id=5225821464</a></p><h2 id="配合APlayer和MetingJS"><a href="#配合APlayer和MetingJS" class="headerlink" title="配合APlayer和MetingJS"></a>配合APlayer和MetingJS</h2><p>经后期测试该API与MetingJS配合的不是很完美。API写法与MetingJS不一致，可能部分功能无法使用，请自行测试调整。<br>仅展示本站使用的吸底模式代码，更多使用方法见下方链接。</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;link rel=<span class="string">&quot;stylesheet&quot;</span> href=<span class="string">&quot;https://api.suiyil.cn/aplayer/dist/APlayer.min.css&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;script src=<span class="string">&quot;https://api.suiyil.cn/aplayer/dist/APlayer.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;meting-js</span><br><span class="line">fixed=<span class="string">&quot;true&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">server=<span class="string">&quot;netease&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">type=<span class="string">&quot;playlist&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">id=<span class="string">&quot;5225821464&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">order=<span class="string">&quot;random&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">preload=<span class="string">&quot;none&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/meting-js&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> meting\_api=<span class="string">&#x27;https://api.suiyil.cn/163-api/?type=:type&amp;id=:id&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;script src=<span class="string">&quot;https://api.suiyil.cn/Meting/Meting.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p>APlayer参数详见 <a href="https://aplayer.js.org/#/zh-Hans/">https://aplayer.js.org/#/zh-Hans/</a><br>MetingJS用法详见 <a href="https://github.com/metowolf/Metingjs">https://github.com/metowolf/Metingjs</a><br>有什么问题欢迎留言询问</p>]]></content>
    
    
